  <summary date="2019-08-23T18:38:32Z" status="Introduced in House">Protecting Benefits for Disabled Veterans Act of 2017

This bill authorizes the Department of Veterans Affairs to determine a veteran with a service-connected disability has a total disability based on his or her ability to secure or maintain substantially gainful employment as a result of the disability.</summary>
